metadata.name: Euphoria House
metadata.description:
Euphoria house has two cores:
In the digital world, represents a unique opportunity to explore a utopian experience in the metaverse;  For the first time we face a space that doesnâ€™t obey physical laws and the question arises: how is architecture built in our dreams? 
This digital house is complemented by a harmonious melody composed by Mistyhop, where the euphoric experience becomes involving and the frequencies will bring inspiration.
In the physical world is an exchange of benefits for the world and wants to value the potential of digital creations to build a better reality. In this way, the profits will be donated for the construction of homes for people in need in Latin America. Donation percentage according to final auction price:
Amounts in USD

From 2kto20k=50%
From 20kto40k=60%
From 40Kto200k=70%
From >200k=80%

The project has been developed by architecture studio Future, who will be in charge of sending the 3D files to the owner in case of an integration in the metaverse.
